# Antigravity Project Context (.agy)

## 📌 Project Overview
- **Name:** Haven Android Client
- **Description:** Android Compose application for the Haven AI Companion.
- **Main Directory:** `C:\Users\admin\source\project-haven-android`

## 🔗 Connected Repositories & Services
- **Showcase Registry:** `C:\Users\admin\source\haven-companions`
- **Active Backend Server:** `C:\Users\admin\haven-server` (Runs on port 18799)

## 🛑 Security Boundaries & No-Fly Zones (CRITICAL)
- **Sensitive Paths:** Never read or expose files from `C:\Users\admin\haven-server\wwwroot\uploads` (contains private/NSFW user assets).
- **Public Assets:** All visual templates/portraits destined for public repositories must be generated using `generate_image` (SFW anime/illustrations only). No desktop screenshots.
- **Scope Restriction:** Do not write C# backend or database migrations unless explicitly requested; keep changes scoped strictly to companion metadata and C# registry logic.
- **Safety Limitations:** To avoid tripping safety filters, do not attempt to automate background device administration, remote software installations, or raw network scans on external hosts.
